# Agent Change Test Gate

Whenever an agent **changes any code** in this repository (adds/edits/deletes code), the agent must run the unit test suite locally and ensure it passes **before ending the task**.

## Required commands (run from repo root)

- **Unit tests must pass**:

```bash
pnpm run test:unit
```

- **Coverage must be checked** (and any negative impact must be called out and addressed when feasible):

```bash
pnpm run test:unit:coverage
```

## Expectations

- Do not skip tests after code changes.
- If tests fail, fix the failures and rerun until passing.
- If coverage changes, report the change and take reasonable steps to prevent regressions (add/adjust tests as appropriate).
